title: Ep. - 219 - CHEER ON NETFLIX REVIEW
description:
6th grader Cooper Muir reviews Gordon Ramsay’s 24 Hours to Hell and Back on Fox. 

 

Judi Brown reviews Cheer on Netflix, a gripping docuseries which follows the ups and downs of Navarro College's competitive cheer squad as they work to win a coveted national title. The show is a behind-the-scenes look at the superhuman athleticism that goes into competitive college cheerleading.

 

Podcast host Sarah Galli reviews Married to Medicine on Bravo.
